comment.body: One item to mention is that `SetProjectDefaults`’s internals are very similar to `SetClusterDefaults`. My normal rule is to wait until doing something at least three times before abstracting it out, but I am very open to abstracting this out now if @acohen4 concurs.

dockertestenv: expose configuration for direct and pgbouncer connections (#9459)

Trying to setup postgres listeners in NewTestPachd. I need access to a
direct and indirect connection for the same database. There was a bunch
of duplicated code in dockertestenv, so I restructured it around setting
up multi-db environments (direct and PGBouncer), with helper functions
for getting one DB vs. the other, or converting the configuration to the
various option formats used through the codebase.
